Jika kita meneruskan siasatan kita,

00:37:51.030 --> 00:37:52.690
bagaimana anda perlu pergi nanti?

00:37:53.440 --> 00:37:55.030
Dia pasti membawa Feng Qingzhuo
bersamanya,

00:37:55.030 --> 00:37:56.510
yang boleh memberi kita masa.

